CardNames.1:
Sycophants

Q: If a player provokes Psionic Outrage once and then Weapon Outrage twice on the same turn, how many ships would Sycophant place?
A: 2 ships total. The 2 ships is once per turn, not once per turn per Outrage.

Q: If this triggers during battle, do the ships I place in the battle system count as attacking ships?
A: No.
